title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week 3
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Rico Bosco needs a bounce back after a 4-11 week and we get a inside scoop from Dave how Big Cat unintentionally made Katie cry on a private jet last weekend.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
